title: JON ROSE'S GAME CHANGER
description: )(20 frontman, Jon Rose, checks in with us to explain how the new 'Game Changer' project is working to bring people together by combining sport and clean drinking water. It really is incredible stuff. Click through for the full story and photos. Video and photos: Tom Aiello
